transcription.text:
Speaker 1: Thank you for calling. This is John. How can I help you?

Speaker 2: Yes, hold on one second.

Speaker 1: Okay, I'm calling because I—

Speaker 2: I unsubscribed because the pills don't work.

Speaker 1: Okay.

Speaker 2: And I got a delivery today of pills.

Speaker 1: Okay, how did you unsubscribe, sir? Because you have to call, and I don't see you've called us.

Speaker 2: I did it online.

Speaker 1: Oh, we don't have a way to do it online. So I need your name and zip code.

Speaker 2: Ah, it must have been a fake site then because... All right. My name is John Humiston.

Speaker 1: H-u-m-i-s-t-o-n.

Speaker 2: Okay, one one three one three five.

Speaker 1: 71 Oswego River Road.

Speaker 2: Correct.

Speaker 1: Okay, I can definitely stop this for you, sir. You said it didn't work?

Speaker 2: No, not at all.

Speaker 1: Not a feeling. And you don't want to try the Cialis either? You just want to be done?

Speaker 2: No, I tried Cialis on my doctor.

Speaker 1: Yeah, and it didn't work.

Speaker 2: Okay. Well, it may be—I mean, I'm not a doctor—but it may be something else is going on

Speaker 1: that's preventing these pills from helping, but I have closed out your account, sir.

Speaker 2: Thank you very much.

Speaker 1: You're welcome. Have a good one.

Speaker 2: You too.
